snippet.title: Annalynn MD - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Play on itch.io: https://cruise-elroy.itch.io/annalynn-md
Play on Newgrounds: https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/974741

​Annalynn MD​ is a brand new falling block puzzle game made in the style of games from the 16-bit era! A miner no more, Annalynn has now joined the world of medicine in pursuit of the ultimate cure! Twist, turn, and take out germs as you help her make the world just a little bit healthier.

Promotional artwork, title screen artwork, and Annalynn sprites by @SparkBag 
Music and some sound effects by @levir.starsmusic
